<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٢١ -<span class="c5"> نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{مَا أَخْلَفْنَا مَوْعِدَكَ بِمَلْكِنَا}</span> <span class="c4">[طه: ٨٧]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«بِطَاقَتِنَا»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>